<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"44893 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default\">\\t</span>&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;The Customer&amp;#39;s loan process will take more days due to any festival.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
