<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"44893 characters\"><span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
<span class=sf-dump-str title=\"44893 characters\">&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Cookies are small files that a site or its service provider transfers to your computer&amp;#39;s hard drive through your web browser with your permission which enables the site or service provider&amp;#39;s systems to recognize your browser and capture and remember certain information. We use cookies to help us understand and save your preferences for future&amp;nbsp;visits, keep track of advertisements and compile aggregate data about site traffic and site interaction so that we can offer better site experiences and tools in the future.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<span class=\"sf-dump-default sf-dump-ns\">\\r\\n</span></span>
